title: 143: The Walmart Haul Episode (May '21 Edition)
itunes:title: The Walmart Haul Episode (May '21 Edition)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa and crew are diving into some tasty (and some not so tasty) food finds from Walmart! Finds like KIND oatmeal, KIND smoothie bowls, plant-based pizza, spreadable feta cheese, HEINZ Kranch, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus the carb-cutting find that will have you running to Walmart ASAP. No time to waste—push play now, and then head on over to the Foodcast page for all the finds mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: The time has come for another Walmart haul, a.k.a. a HaulMart!
